room_title: Escape room "The High School Mystery" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
review: We had a great time escaping the High School Mystery room! The staff was wonderful, and the room was challenging! Can't wait to go back!

room_title: Escape room "The High School Mystery" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
review: It was our first time here we did the scooby doo themed room and escaped with 5 minutes left great experience and fun time definitely coming back...

room_title: Escape room "The High School Mystery" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
review: We just went through the Scooby Doo themed room and it was fun! A great family activity that gets you thinking.

room_title: Escape room "The High School Mystery" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Wilmington in Wilmington (DE)
review: Kids and I just did the Scooby-Doo inspired room. I thought it would be easy, but omg! I was with daughter, 16, and son, 11, we did not complete, but were soooo close. We needed about 5 more minutes...it was a blast, will definitely go back with friends!
